text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_SofiaIntro {
	"Do you know how you can avoid
	getting lost in the mountains?

	You can bend twigs as trail
	markers."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_SofiaDefeat {
	"Ohhh!
	I did my best!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_SofiaPostBattle {
	"I want to go home!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_DudleyIntro {
	"Hahaha!
	Can you beat my power?"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_DudleyDefeat {
	"Oops!
	Outmuscled!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_DudleyPostBattle {
	"I go for power because I hate
	thinking."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_CooperIntro {
	"You have a POKéDEX?
	I want one, too."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_CooperDefeat {
	"Shoot!
	I am so jealous!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_CooperPostBattle {
	"When you finish your POKéDEX,
	can I have it?"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_SteveIntro {
	"Um… Do you know about POKéMON
	cosplay?"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_SteveDefeat {
	"Well, that's that."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_StevePostBattle {
	"POKéMON cosplay is dressing up as
	POKéMON for fun.

	CLEFAIRY is a favorite."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_AllenIntro {
	"My POKéMON techniques will leave
	you crying!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_AllenDefeat {
	"I give!
	You're a better technician!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_AllenPostBattle {
	"In mountains, you'll often find
	ROCK-type POKéMON."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_MarthaIntro {
	"I don't often come here, but I will
	battle you."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_MarthaDefeat {
	"Oh!
	I lost!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_MarthaPostBattle {
	"I like tiny POKéMON.
	Big ones are too scary!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_EricIntro {
	"Hit me with your best shot!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_EricDefeat {
	"Fired away!"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_EricPostBattle {
	"I'll raise my POKéMON to beat
	yours, kid."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_WinstonIntro {
	"I draw illustrations of POKéMON
	when I'm home."
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_WinstonDefeat {
	"Whew…
	I'm exhausted…"
}

text RockTunnel_B1F_Text_WinstonPostBattle {
	"I'm an artist, not a fighter.
	I'll go home to draw."
}
